@Goethe
#A man of pleasure is a man of pains.
@Edward Young
#People hate those who that make them feel their own
inferiority: therefore conceal all your learning carefully.
@Lord Chesterfield
#How bitter a thing it is to look into happiness
through another man's eyes!
@William Shakespeare
#Envy is better worth having than pity.
@proverb
#For one man who sincerely pities our misfortunes,
there are a thousand who sincerely hate our success.
@Charles Colton
